title: Lynda.com - Element 3D Essential Training [TDM}
description:
Element 3D Essential Training

Element 3D Essential Training - a 4-hour online training course by Lynda.com
Element 3D is a third-party plugin that allows actual 3D models to be created from scratch or exported to Adobe After Effects, and rendered and composited at a high level of quality and impressive speed. Element 3D Essential Training walks you throug.

This online tutorial was officially released on February 11, 2013..

The course covers Video, Motion Graphics, Adobe, Video Copilot, After Effects, Element 3D.
